environment.name: house
environment.description:
Large house environment with all of the base objects in their normal place.
All of the other house environments are based off this with any combination
of objects, object positions, & lighting changed

format.name: object_map_ground_truth
format.description:
A ground truth "object map" servers is similar to the standard "object map" 
map, but is meant for use when specifying ground truth maps. The objects in 
the map:
  - have a class label rather than probability distribution),  
  - have a field for denoting an object's unique ID, and
  - can denote if the object is a group
